      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface reflects meticulous care, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior. Mechanically unrivaled and maintained to the highest standards, this motorcar offers an investment-grade driving experience for the discerning collector. We invite you to experience a standard of excellence that transcends the typical pre-owned market.",
