    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this beauty! It is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells just like it did the day it left the showroom. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so you won\u2019t find a single blemish inside or out. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone to take it on a new adventure. You really have to see it in person to believe how spotless it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
